[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     60[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### Issue 5: `get_pathway_recommendations` Evaluates All Conditions Per Edge Individually But Reports Aggregate
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     61[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
